<br>
Can you bind wounds on horseback? Seeing as you are considered to be sitting for meditation purposes you could gain hp with bind and med at the same time if you can bind on horseback.<br>
<br>
To make the bind wound skill viable we would need to heal much more then per bind.<br>
<br>
if we were at 2x bind wound healing rate it would be 30 hp a tick or 10 mana per tick still a loss of 5-10 mana for sitting.<br>
<br>
if we were at 3x bind wound healing rate or 45hp a tick that would be 15 mana per tick and a loss of 0-5 and probably a reasonable alternative.<br>
<br>
So mage bandages could be changed to heal more per bandage or bind wounds could scale up with level to heal more and not just skill cap.  Highly unlikely they will do such a thing. Too bad it looked like a nice skill to have.<br>
